dcterms:description: The dataset from semanticscholar was acquired with several search queries on the open API, returning a format in JSON that is easily computed for further inquiry. The search terms are formed by a list of keywords in combination with all years from 1970 to 2017, resulting in 26940 unique entries.
dcterms:title: Semanticscholar Data

dcterms:description: The dataset from the Bibliography on Genetic Programming had an artifact, a strong decline from 1999 to 2000 in GA publications could be seen. The database was filtered to discard publications without the keyword 'genetic programming'.
dcterms:title: Bibliography on Genetic Programming
